{
  "stem": "11205.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "That's why he asked where I come from, who is [? here. ?] And then we discover we are both Jewish.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we start to go out together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We-- we worked shifts.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He was working like from 7:00-- three shifts from 7:00 till 4:00 one week, next week from 4:00 to 12:00, and the third week from 12:00 to 7:00 in the morning.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So whenever he worked till 4:00, we met.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we-- we went out together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Then he proposed to me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And we married-- we knew each other only five months, and because New Year's Eve is the day we both had this evening free, so he suggested we get married that evening, because we will maybe celebrate together.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I had-- and I had a huppah there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was an older Jewish man, which had a huppah, because he-- actually in Russia, you don't need to register.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I thought how could-- I will come home something to register without a huppah.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I still felt it should be.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I had a huppah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- Did you-- did you have a party?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "How was it?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A party-- you know, I was so friendly where I worked in this canteen that they'd been stealing for-- for me meat and-- and beer.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't do nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- the staff and from the-- the manager from where the storeroom-- the-- beer because the students want to celebrate.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they had a-- each two-liter beer and a-- and a dinner that came.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So instead beer-- so they took it out beer and poured water there to have the amount.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they-- they were very, very-- they liked me there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was-- they were very friendly to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You said-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
